{"type": "article", "id": 46831, "title": "Teen Vogue 停刊， 以及，大阪有家藏书25万的二手书店 ︳浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-11-03T03:29:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 16156, "name": "Acne Studios"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 45235, "name": "TSUTAYA"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 12966, "name": "Teen Vogue"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171103111325Zz7YxfKUvS2NChRE.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/quality-of-sales-help-ralph-lauren-over-deliver-on-q2-results-11041402/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Ralph Lauren 第二季度净利润大涨</strong></a> ︳第二季度内，Ralph Lauren 的净利润同比暴涨 212%，至 1.43 亿美元，但销售额同比减少了 8.6%，至 16.6 亿美元。品牌首席执行官 Patrice Louvet 在电话会议上强调，中国是最具潜力的市场。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/loreal-sales-decline-0-9-in-q3-11040875/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>欧莱雅集团发财报，高端化妆品部门和亚洲市场成主要推动力</strong></a> ︳截止至 9 月 30 日的第三个季度内，欧莱雅集团销售额同比上涨 5.1%，至 61 亿欧元，略高于分析师预期的 60.8 亿欧元。其中包括 YSL、兰蔻和 Giorgio Armani 在内的高端化妆品部门销售额涨幅最大，上涨了 11.2% 至 20.2 亿欧元，涨幅远高于消费品部门的 2.3%。按地区分，集团在新兴市场销售额增长最为显著，为 10.2％。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/11/02/business/media/conde-nast-teen-vogue.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><em>Teen Vogue</em> 停刊，康泰纳仕将继续裁员 </strong></a>︳康泰纳仕传媒集团宣布，每年发行五期的 <em>Teen Vogue</em> 将停止纸质版，并计划于下周四之前裁员 80 名，约占员工总数的 2.5%。另外，集团旗下的 <em>GQ、Glamour、Allure</em> 以及 <em>Architectural Digest</em> 将从一年 12 期减少至 11 期；<em>Bon Appétit</em> 将从一年 11 期减少至 10 期；<em>W</em> 和 <em>CondéNast Traveler</em> 将从一年 10 期减少至 8 期。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>最近，草间弥生的<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/11/02/yayoi-kusama-festival-of-life-nyc-exhibit/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Festival of Life 和 Infinity Nets </a>来到了纽约，分别于切尔西和上东区办展。外媒评论，草间弥生的展览是个“Instagrammable”的自拍圣地。来看看：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105535huUmvrsCqRPApQzM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105535qVmL7hH6xbSW2BCw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105536ath7SZyvdo9Qf6UD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105538eOhPXiRfN2gDqMTA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105540jnS6uFiotqeZAEKI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017110310554151vSRB4aAGZCWY7j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105546OqPM2Dzj5F6AUtIB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017110310554974hda2CetGb6mYTE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105549d1fpBIlcH6mW0YML.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105551AR6oXDGebKuldqNp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031055517CQgFl0KoIW6NxOq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105554heLN7MH8FvxOEZR0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/11/02/balenciaga-just-dropped-dark-new-capsule-collection-sinners/#slide-11\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga </a>将发售一个以 Sinners 命名的新系列，不过也没什么特别的，主要产品就是写着 Sinners 字样的帽衫、卫衣、牛仔夹克、水洗牛仔裤和棒球帽。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105728ejgHKDuXkB3EbRLv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031057284CPJ6KfV2kGlzqcL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105729uirP3lb2pBcTnovN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105729sGrmEicuZvlOhzHK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105734uoL8sF2rRqCBSjXG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105735kiM5EzfTtgFjChoD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031057360gmIJxGskwzMoKrB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105730ztYXg06nk1Z9VpNF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017110310573589fk6XRB7rYIKVEH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105729vyXar9PzDQhWon1k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105739ycmPxZSCQD654EHY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>D<a href=\"http://highfashionliving.com/dos-studio-fallwinter-2018-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">os Studio </a>是一个今年新创立的西班牙品牌。第一个系列就是 2018 秋冬男装系列，还蛮好看的。<br> </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031058074f07Rb9EylahepqK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105807ZEeaF1ALGRIjDk6v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105809G25JqBptkEgRfclA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105812VoGthObcuBMRwxzX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105812cryCIdWDi8gVTR41.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/11/acne-studios-diner-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Acne Studios</a> 最近发布了一个以 Dinner 为名的系列，推出了一系列印有唇膏、冰块、磁带、电话等印花图案的帽衫、卫衣、T 恤，还有手袋、钱包、钥匙圈等小东西。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031058213M96GSQI4uXPBWep.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017110310582135igVQYX0aLDbEur.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105821E1qTYuRVL6HCrxgA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105821uc4I5x3HSoETa0QF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105821MwanJBzNefCm7TIi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665975\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105826zqc9sALabhOelmEo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103105826lQ894UMcLivIyAFd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>adidas 官方发布了与 Pharrell Williams 共同打造的 N.E.R.D NMD Hu 鞋款：右脚上印着 Y.O.U，左脚是 N.E.R.D。它将于这周六登陆 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/08/24/complexcon-2017-lineup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ComplexCon</a> 独家发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110255q2FRJzDg8T0mwb65.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110256WPzXi6tjNeLkA3wJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>11 月 1 日，日本生活方式品牌 TSUTAYA（蔦屋） 在大阪开设了一家全新业态的店铺 <a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/504766\" rel=\"nofollow\">TSUTAYA BOOK GARAGE</a>。 TSUTAYA BOOK GARAGE 于去年在福冈开设了第一家店，这是首次来到大阪。</p><p>大阪的这家书店占地 1800 平米，约有 25 万册二手书籍，另外也贩售 DVD、CD、游戏和部分新书。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110950x238WmarXRcZ6Jt9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110951EnA8wxpq5VLm13ut.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110952qZcTh5Ld8tAnprVs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110953CsfUxko3zZy67m8i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103110953PDM51tXVrpflxuvG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：TSUTAYA BOOK GARAGE</p>"}